d without paying forever.</strong></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg0ZUVz69s3_text","label":"gg0ZUVz69s3_text","default":"1. Drugstore creams never reach the layer where aging actually happens"},{"type":"html","id":"gglJPlI9mC4_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gglJPlI9mC4_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/1_d7e9343c-f537-467d-a217-e889282258f9.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"ggeNNIcscpb_text","label":"ggeNNIcscpb_text","default":"<span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:36px;\"><strong>1. Drugstore creams never reach the layer where aging actually happens</strong></span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYNTDnIV-v_text","label":"ggYNTDnIV-v_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:18px;\">I started here like most men do. Grabbed Cerave, Kiels and Nivea, figured it had good reviews. Eight weeks later my skin felt softer in the morning — that was it. Turns out these creams coat the surface with silicones and petroleum and evaporate by morning. They never reach the dermis, the layer where wrinkles and sagging actually happen.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gggKNSj0LQp_text","label":"gggKNSj0LQp_text","default":"2. Beef tallow moisturizes. That's it."},{"type":"html","id":"gg_CIxRnYEt_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg_CIxRnYEt_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/landing_1_b_2.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCMUxlXdbt_text","label":"ggCMUxlXdbt_text","default":"<span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:36px;\"><strong>2. Beef tallow moisturizes. That's it.</strong></span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggu3VfflfRH_text","label":"ggu3VfflfRH_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:18px;\">My son sent me a link. Natural, ancestral, no chemicals — I gave it a shot. It wasn't unpleasant, I'll say that. But after eight weeks the lines and sag were exactly where they started. Tallow contains zero active anti-aging ingredients — nothing that signals your skin to rebuild collagen. You're greasing the engine but never turning the key. Oh, and you're going to smell funny for a few hours.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggl9xnciPT8_text","label":"ggl9xnciPT8_text","default":"3. American retinol is destroying the collagen it's supposed to rebuild"},{"type":"html","id":"ggIYq8m62nj_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggIYq8m62nj_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/landing_3_b_1.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"ggcCs4zGVXd_text","label":"ggcCs4zGVXd_text","default":"<span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:36px;\"><strong>3. American retinol is destroying the collagen it's supposed to rebuild</strong></span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTzDhLq9no_text","label":"ggTzDhLq9no_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:18px;\">I had high hopes for this one. Everything I read said retinol was the gold standard. Two weeks in my face was red, raw, and peeling. I pushed through. The structural changes I was looking for — jawline, deep lines — essentially unchanged. Here's why: American drugstore retinol uses aggressive synthetic enhancers that tear through your skin barrier and trigger inflammation. That inflammation activates enzymes that actively break down collagen. The ingredient meant to rebuild your face is simultaneously destroying it. Most men try it once and never touch it again.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7OvzNDy45_text","label":"gg7OvzNDy45_text","default":"4. Botox freezes muscles. It doesn't fix anything."},{"type":"html","id":"ggBnM9iKPKY_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggBnM9iKPKY_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/4_39dff8d9-6c90-4564-8baf-0b085a9df77f.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"ggcBC2sdY_f_text","label":"ggcBC2sdY_f_text","default":"<span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:36px;\"><strong>4. Botox freezes muscles. It doesn't fix anything.</strong></span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggKdf8Q9rjR_text","label":"ggKdf8Q9rjR_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:18px;\">I talked to three men my age who'd been using Botox for two years or more. It works — expression lines genuinely smooth out. But it costs $300–$600 every three months, does not stimulate collagen, and the moment you stop paying the results disappear. All three said unprompted they wished they'd found something else first. $2,400 a year to manage a problem you're not actually solving.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7X3POWBG0_text","label":"gg7X3POWBG0_text","default":"5. No Chinese 'mystery chemicals' — just the same Italian ingredients from the same Italian farm for 38 years"},{"type":"html","id":"ggPrdleLjrE_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggPrdleLjrE_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/landing_5_1.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"gggcVgbI9-J_text","label":"gggcVgbI9-J_text","default":"<span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:36px;\"><strong>5. No Chinese 'mystery chemicals' — just the same Italian ingredients from the same Italian farm for 38 years</strong></span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggML05UEnV0_text","label":"ggML05UEnV0_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:18px;\">Most skincare brands in the USA don't actually make their own products — they call a contract manufacturer, source cheap ingredients from overseas, bulk the formula out with fillers, and bury a fraction of the active ingredient at the bottom of a thirty-item list. SerlinoLab has never worked that way because the supply chain simply won't allow it. Every batch comes from the same family-owned lab that's been running since 1987, using local ingredients from a farm just down the road. It’s been operating since 1987</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxBwtTZ-6w_text","label":"ggxBwtTZ-6w_text","default":"6. Retinyl palmitate — the Gentleman's Retinol"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqWFwZagKP_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggqWFwZagKP_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/landing_5_7.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"ggXuRcE0Hz4_text","label":"ggXuRcE0Hz4_text","default":"<span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:36px;\"><strong>6. Retinyl palmitate — the Gentleman's Retinol</strong></span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggNz49II8W3_text","label":"ggNz49II8W3_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:18px;\">SerlinoLab's active ingredient is retinyl palmitate — known as the Gentleman's Retinol. It sends the same collagen-rebuilding signal as prescription retinol but through a slow enzymatic conversion once it's already inside the skin. No barrier damage. No inflammatory response. No redness, no peeling, no purging phase. The right ingredient, finally delivered the right way.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggebstfB6aV_text","label":"ggebstfB6aV_text","default":"7. Cold-pressed Italian olive oil — sourced from the Italian countryside near the lab"},{"type":"html","id":"ggEk4WdlhpH_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggEk4WdlhpH_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/landing_5_6.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"ggXxNdYYPBH_text","label":"ggXxNdYYPBH_text","default":"<span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:36px;\"><strong>7. Cold-pressed Italian olive oil — sourced from the Italian countryside near the lab</strong></span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggL68alHC7p_text","label":"ggL68alHC7p_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:18px;\">This is the delivery system that changes everything. Its lipid structure mirrors the natural fats in male skin exactly — so the actives travel through your skin's own channels rather than forcing their way in. Absorbs completely in seconds. Zero grease. Keeps working for 6–8 hours while you sleep.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg-8U0W5kdu_text","label":"gg-8U0W5kdu_text","default":"8. 20 seconds before bed. 2,920 hours of repair a year."},{"type":"html","id":"ggi93ATFmN1_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggi93ATFmN1_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/8_2e9c1452-c5c9-4d5a-b30e-07152b59d946.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQfwy1RC7O_text","label":"ggQfwy1RC7O_text","default":"<span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:36px;\"><strong>8. 20 seconds before bed. 2,920 hours of repair a year.</strong></span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggfFrPnlfkk_text","label":"ggfFrPnlfkk_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:18px;\">8 hours of sleep, 365 nights — that is 2,920 hours your skin has to rebuild every year. SerlinoLab keeps working through every one of them. Botox wears off. Retinol sits inert after an hour. Drugstore creams evaporate before you wake up. SerlinoLab is the only option still working at hour eight. That compounding effect is why the results don't fade — because you are actually rebuilding structure, not managing the surface.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggiee9OjDZI_text","label":"ggiee9OjDZI_text","default":"9. 73,000+ Italian men. Recommended by pharmacists across Italy."},{"type":"html","id":"ggxgaaQzQ1A_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggxgaaQzQ1A_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/landing_9_1.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLQq6kd4KT_text","label":"ggLQq6kd4KT_text","default":"<span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:36px;\"><strong>9. 73,000+ Italian men. Recommended by pharmacists across Italy.</strong></span>"},{"type":